      <p></p><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-style: solid; border-top-width: 4px; border-top-color: #a4d530; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #d5d3b8; padding: 1em; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; overflow: auto;"><h3>It's Our 60th Anniversary!</h3><h3><a href="http://www.bpl.bc.ca/events/60th-anniversary" title="Burnaby Public Library's 60th Anniversary"><img src="/sites/default/files/uploads/images/general/anniversary-logo-small.png" width="117" height="106" class="image-right" style="font-size: 1.31em; line-height: 1.18;" alt="Burnaby Public Library's 60th anniversary logo" /></a></h3><p>2016 marks 60 years since Burnaby Public Library first opened, and we invite you to join us in celebrating this milestone! Throughout the year, we're hosting special programs and events at all BPL branches, and throughout the City of Burnaby, too. Visit <a href="http://www.bpl.bc.ca/events/60th-anniversary" title="Burnaby Public Library's 60th Anniversary page">Our 60th Anniversary</a> page for updates.</p></div>  
